---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead
			title="About — Andrew Vieau"
			description="I'm a technical trainer & sales engineer based in Big Lake, Minnesota."
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>About</h1>

			<p>
				I've spent the last 11 years moving back and forth between Technical training roles and
				Sales Engineering.
			</p>

			<p>
				On the technical side, I'm a full stack web developer with a long background on the web. I joined the enterprise space just in time to witness the move away from on-premise, monolithic software to cloud-native, composable platforms.
			</p>

			<p>
				On the people side, I've trained just about every kind of audience: marketers, technical teams, developers, new hires, and seasoned professionals, both customer-facing and internal. I've delivered live workshops in person and remotely, built self-paced eLearning courses, and covered everything from onboarding to ongoing enablement. I've also hired, onboarded, and managed a team of technical trainers & learning experience designers along the way.
			</p>

			<p>
				Like everyone in the tech space right now, since last year I've been leaning heavily into AI for both business and personal projects. Using LLMs to accelerate
				content creation, AI video tools to quickly produce scalable eLearning content, and
				conversation intelligence platforms to extract insights from sales cycles and sharpen how
				I engage with prospects.
			</p>

			<p>
What ties it all together is a genuine love of making complex things understandable. I've spent over a decade working with bleeding-edge enterprise tech that is rarely simple to explain. My favorite moment is seeing that person who was struggling to understand a concept — whether in a workshop or a sales demo — when everything finally clicks.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>